General.Name: Finnovate Acquisition Corp. Warrants
General.Description: Finnovate Acquisition Corp. focuses on entering into a merger, share exchange, asset acquisition, share purchase, recapitalization, reorganization, or other similar business combination with one or more businesses or entities. It intends to focus its search on companies that provide technological services to the financial services industry. The company was incorporated in 2021 and is based in George Town, the Cayman Islands.
